      "content": "That makes sense. I want to get more specific for the module though. Could you give some more detailed advice on hair? Like, what kind of styles should people go for to stay within that 'polished' look? Also, how should we advise people on accessories or headwear to make sure they don't look too casual or distracting in those settings?",
